attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Classic Realty NW - Ely

data.description: This 3BR/2 BA home located in Vail's Addition to Ely is a great option for anyone looking for convenience and comfort. It's just steps away from the Trezona Trail and close to Shagawa Lake! Upon entering you'll find a large mudroom with plenty of storage as well as a bright and cozy kitchen nook area complete with built-ins. This kitchen has been recently updated with new flooring, counter tops, fresh paint and new cabinet hardware for a stylish finish. On the main floor is a 3/4 bath with beautiful tile work and a large walk-in shower. From the kitchen you can access the sunny dining room which opens to a living room with great views! The master bedroom features a barnwood door with the two other bedrooms offering hardwood floors. Downstairs you'll find another 3/4 bath as well as 1 1/2 car garage. With so many wonderful features, this home won't last long. Schedule your viewing today and come see it for yourself!
